{"tid":211867,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"山下智久教你「正確吃香腸」！合體龜梨和也、松本潤3帥撩妹","createTime":"2017-04-22T03:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T14:51:48.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a85b884bc2e435d80eecf8c7e3d2ea7980bc842c","tid":211867,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"日本傑尼斯男星龜梨和也、山下智久相隔12年再合體，主演新日劇《真命天菜》掀起追劇熱潮。兩人為了宣傳新戲特地參加綜藝《嵐的大挑戰》（嵐にしやがれ），和松本潤一起表演帥哥的生活技能，尤其教學「帥哥開香腸」、「帥哥倒豆乳」、「帥哥打包行李」等，3男神穿西裝罕見同框，一起擺POSE更電翻大批粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBA5GFT.img?h=486&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBA5GFT.img%3Fh%3D486%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=f433e180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲山下智久、龜梨和也、松本潤3男神合體，傳授帥哥生活技巧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2474/d2474144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2474%2Fd2474144.jpg&h=d6e3fb3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲山下智久教你用牙籤開吃香腸。<br />\n<br />\n松本潤的單元「THIS IS MJ」專門分享帥哥生活技能，例如肚子餓了，面對日本最夯美食「魚肉香腸」，正在苦惱怎麼開吃時，山下智久現身用一根牙籤就打開外包裝。而他被2位師弟喊「前輩」，自然也獻上「倒豆乳」的方式，原來盒裝瓶口不要太靠近杯口，反轉朝上就能帥氣倒出豆乳，令觀眾嘖嘖稱奇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2474/d2474142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2474%2Fd2474142.jpg&h=108cf2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲松本潤一個轉瓶口動作，就能帥帥地倒出豆乳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2474/d2474143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2474%2Fd2474143.jpg&h=dc26f223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲龜梨和也帥氣折衣服「還能丟哦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後是打包行李，龜梨和也將衣服折成捲筒狀，笑稱「拿來丟也完全OK。」3大男神正坐POSE超帥氣，最後完成3種帥技，反觀C朗拿度及美斯，歐聯場均入球率是0.74球及0.82球，不及法卡奧。松本潤忍不住笑說：「這個單元好像主婦的智慧！」影片在網路瘋傳，粉絲直呼「太帥」、「豪華陣容」、「每招都好好用啊！」"},{"pid":"cffb7122cc80386ae8c27c5369965ffbd843ff0d","tid":211867,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb7a79617bef3464b44bf570c1fad4a2273f845","tid":211867,"uid":4058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"婦人的生活智囊"},{"pid":"54b977e613271157fcff8c8c1f1cc4d4c6c40133","tid":211867,"uid":6880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"最接近神既男人"},{"pid":"2fff1a38fb2dc5fc46eaf6614acdd0565f8701d1","tid":211867,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3大男神正坐POSE超帥氣，最後完成3種帥技，<span style=\"color: red;\">反觀C朗拿度及美斯，歐聯場均入球率是0.74球及0.82球，不及法卡奧。</span>松本潤忍不住笑說：「這個單元好像主婦的智慧！"},{"pid":"ed9295c1e5769638ae5221fef7165a9fe63430a5","tid":211867,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"而家先興食魚肉香腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef59a3f17c3309e245bf146f61ab103df33328ee","tid":211867,"uid":71884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02bd070a26b9fa84b68d23896e8a8a1c1541749","tid":211867,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"千雪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb86b969a58c4e0a33a5229c2ea34c7bf30d2cb","tid":211867,"uid":32211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千雪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n變左馬壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},